#06/24/2012
Added recover password via mail system


#E-Mail Recover PWD System
In order to make the system functional in your localhost
we will set an email server in the 1025 port of the localhost

Set-up your settings.py project folder with 
the EMAIL_PORT for the email server

$ vim settings.py
Add the following line:
EMAIL_PORT = 1025

Start a SMTP dummy server
$python -m smtpd -n -c DebuggingServer localhost:1025
